1
00:00:05,665 --> 00:00:08,361
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,434 --> 00:00:12,302
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,372 --> 00:00:16,365
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,709 --> 00:00:19,200
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,279 --> 00:00:23,340
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,416 --> 00:00:27,375
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,855 --> 00:00:33,588
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,294 --> 00:00:37,263
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,699 --> 00:00:41,792
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,535 --> 00:00:43,832
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:46,730
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,781 --> 00:01:00,151
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,353 --> 00:01:01,513
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,588 --> 00:01:05,388
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,725 --> 00:01:10,924
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,197 --> 00:01:12,528
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,599 --> 00:01:13,998
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,067 --> 00:01:20,336
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:31,351 --> 00:01:33,251
And the next match.

20
00:01:34,387 --> 00:01:37,379
This year's rookie looks challenging...

21
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:44,920
Naruto Uzumaki vs. Kiba Inuzuka

22
00:01:45,365 --> 00:01:47,629
It's here, it's here, it's here!

23
00:01:47,801 --> 00:01:49,496
What we've been waiting for!

24
00:01:49,870 --> 00:01:51,963
It's finally my turn!

25
00:01:52,372 --> 00:01:54,533
Yeah! Lucky us!

26
00:01:54,708 --> 00:01:57,575
If it's this guy,
we'll absolutely win, Akamaru!

27
00:02:00,213 --> 00:02:03,478
<i>Show us how much you've grown.</i>

28
00:02:07,387 --> 00:02:08,684
I'm going to do it!

29
00:02:09,923 --> 00:02:15,862
Akamaru Unleashed!
Who's Top Dog Now?

30
00:02:17,330 --> 00:02:21,790
The seventh battle,
Naruto Uzumaki versus Kiba Inuzuka.

31
00:02:34,614 --> 00:02:36,377
I got sick of waiting!

32
00:02:36,816 --> 00:02:40,081
It's finally time for me to shine!
Believe it!

33
00:02:41,788 --> 00:02:43,085
That's my line!

34
00:02:43,256 --> 00:02:45,224
With you as my opponent,
I've as good as won!

35
00:02:45,325 --> 00:02:46,314
Right, Akamaru?

36
00:02:48,428 --> 00:02:50,453
Don't get excited!

37
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:52,860
You won't be able to beat me!

38
00:02:52,966 --> 00:02:54,399
Why you little...!

39
00:02:56,069 --> 00:02:58,503
Hey! Don't bring your puppy!

40
00:02:58,705 --> 00:03:00,138
He'll get in the way of the match!

41
00:03:00,407 --> 00:03:01,465
You fool!

42
00:03:01,541 --> 00:03:03,270
Akamaru's going to fight with me.

43
00:03:04,644 --> 00:03:06,908
Hey, hey! Is that okay?

44
00:03:07,514 --> 00:03:08,071
Yes.

45
00:03:08,348 --> 00:03:11,317
Animals and insects are treated
the same as ninja tools.

46
00:03:12,118 --> 00:03:13,642
There's no problem.

47
00:03:16,022 --> 00:03:17,421
Well, that's fine!

48
00:03:17,824 --> 00:03:19,792
It's a perfect handicap!

49
00:03:19,993 --> 00:03:21,893
Talking tough!

50
00:03:22,495 --> 00:03:23,291
Then...

51
00:03:24,464 --> 00:03:26,432
Akamaru, don't put a paw in this.

52
00:03:26,933 --> 00:03:28,025
I'll fight him by myself!

53
00:03:29,469 --> 00:03:32,097
Naruto! Don't lose to a guy like this!

54
00:03:33,473 --> 00:03:34,735
<i>It's finally come.</i>

55
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,103
<i>Naruto, huh?</i>

56
00:03:41,181 --> 00:03:43,877
<i>I'm sorry, but he can't beat Kiba...</i>

57
00:03:45,085 --> 00:03:45,813
<i>Kakashi.</i>

58
00:03:46,486 --> 00:03:47,282
<i>Naruto...</i>

59
00:03:47,687 --> 00:03:49,484
<i>I-I want to support you, but...</i>

60
00:03:49,623 --> 00:03:52,820
<i>Kiba's on my team...</i>

61
00:03:55,095 --> 00:03:56,858
<i>Kiba will get mad...</i>

62
00:03:57,864 --> 00:03:58,489
<i>But...</i>

63
00:04:02,569 --> 00:04:03,399
<i>Naruto...</i>

64
00:04:04,904 --> 00:04:07,429
Kiba's lucky.

65
00:04:07,641 --> 00:04:08,232
Hah!

66
00:04:10,844 --> 00:04:15,872
<i>Hah! I don't know how strong he's become</i>
<i>since this guy became a Genin...</i>

67
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:18,980
<i>Today we'll run through Transformation Jutsu.</i>

68
00:04:19,252 --> 00:04:21,049
<i>You'll change yourself into Lord Hokage...</i>

69
00:04:22,288 --> 00:04:24,279
<i>His ability was "that," so...</i>

70
00:04:29,462 --> 00:04:30,326
Transform!

71
00:04:40,473 --> 00:04:41,770
So noisy...

72
00:04:41,941 --> 00:04:43,602
I was sleeping comfortably...

73
00:04:46,546 --> 00:04:49,709
T-That was a joke!
I-I did it on purpose!

74
00:04:49,916 --> 00:04:51,611
Enough, Naruto!

75
00:04:51,851 --> 00:04:53,910
It's your third year
at the academy!

76
00:04:53,987 --> 00:04:54,681
Wha?

77
00:04:55,622 --> 00:04:58,056
Goodness sake, who is that guy?

78
00:04:59,459 --> 00:05:02,292
We've just switched to this class
and already found someone funny.

79
00:05:02,362 --> 00:05:04,762
That guy, he's on a roll.

80
00:05:06,633 --> 00:05:07,895
He's an attention-seeker, huh?

81
00:05:08,568 --> 00:05:10,399
One more time, fool!

82
00:05:11,337 --> 00:05:12,099
Transform!

83
00:05:21,247 --> 00:05:22,043
You...

84
00:05:22,949 --> 00:05:24,473
Is it possible...?

85
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,327
Hey hey, are you serious?

86
00:05:35,528 --> 00:05:38,520
You've been here for three years and
can't even do a respectable transformation?

87
00:05:41,034 --> 00:05:43,229
All of you watch now!

88
00:05:43,570 --> 00:05:47,939
I will absolutely someday become
the true and a real Hokage!

89
00:05:50,343 --> 00:05:51,275
Lame!

90
00:05:51,511 --> 00:05:52,842
What Hokage?!

91
00:06:01,287 --> 00:06:02,754
Some sympathy at the very least...

92
00:06:02,989 --> 00:06:05,253
I'll do you in, in one clean blow!

93
00:06:05,525 --> 00:06:10,792
Really? But you can't beat me!

94
00:06:11,097 --> 00:06:13,531
I said not to act tough.

95
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:23,932
Well then. Please begin!

96
00:06:25,612 --> 00:06:28,240
<i>Ninja Art of Beast Mimicry.</i>
<i>All Four Jutsu!</i>

97
00:06:35,255 --> 00:06:35,983
Here I come!

98
00:06:40,693 --> 00:06:41,523
Fast!

99
00:06:53,273 --> 00:06:57,539
It will be a while'til
he opens his eyes, Mr. Proctor.

100
00:06:57,977 --> 00:06:59,239
Just as I thought.

101
00:06:59,479 --> 00:07:02,448
That Naruto can't be equal to Kiba.

102
00:07:02,782 --> 00:07:03,578
Naruto...

103
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:05,640
That was too embarrassing to watch.

104
00:07:07,654 --> 00:07:08,882
See...

105
00:07:09,556 --> 00:07:12,548
What was that?
That guy is weak.

106
00:07:17,697 --> 00:07:18,595
<i>Naruto!</i>

107
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,591
Huh?

108
00:07:27,507 --> 00:07:28,531
<i>Yes, that's it...</i>

109
00:07:37,617 --> 00:07:38,982
<i>I'll surpass Hokage!</i>

110
00:07:39,719 --> 00:07:44,884
<i>Then everyone in the village will</i>
<i>acknowledge my existence!</i>

111
00:07:45,892 --> 00:07:46,916
<i>Those are his words...</i>

112
00:07:47,493 --> 00:07:49,723
<i>I've always made fun of them, too.</i>

113
00:07:53,066 --> 00:07:57,230
<i>This is the Jonin...a true Ninja...</i>

114
00:07:57,971 --> 00:07:58,869
<i>I have to escape...</i>

115
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:00,599
<i>If I stay like this...</i>

116
00:08:01,140 --> 00:08:04,940
<i>I'll really, really be killed!</i>

117
00:08:06,346 --> 00:08:07,608
<i>Are you hurt...</i>

118
00:08:09,549 --> 00:08:10,743
<i>Scaredy cat?</i>

119
00:08:12,452 --> 00:08:14,784
<i>You just need to become</i>
<i>stronger than me!</i>

120
00:08:25,531 --> 00:08:27,021
<i>Damn you!</i>

121
00:08:28,801 --> 00:08:29,699
<i>You!</i>

122
00:08:29,769 --> 00:08:31,361
<i>What are you doing all of a sudden?!</i>

123
00:08:35,508 --> 00:08:44,212
<i>T-This stupid coward is...</i>
<i>absolutely...not the Sasuke I know!</i>

124
00:08:45,218 --> 00:08:46,446
<i>Don't mess with me!</i>

125
00:08:51,257 --> 00:08:52,622
W-What?

126
00:08:54,761 --> 00:08:56,490
<i>But, it was wrong!</i>

127
00:09:03,369 --> 00:09:04,097
<i>Hey...</i>

128
00:09:05,371 --> 00:09:06,804
<i>are you hurt?</i>

129
00:09:09,709 --> 00:09:10,869
<i>Scaredy cat?</i>

130
00:09:21,321 --> 00:09:26,088
<i>I won't change my words,</i>
<i>that's my way of Ninja!</i>

131
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:41,136
<i>Naruto...</i>

132
00:09:41,874 --> 00:09:43,466
<i>Say it to everyone!</i>

133
00:09:45,411 --> 00:09:46,309
Don't...

134
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:48,512
Don't...

135
00:09:49,282 --> 00:09:50,544
underestimate me!

136
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:55,985
Yeah!

137
00:09:57,290 --> 00:09:59,087
<i>He seems to have grown</i>
<i>to say such thing.</i>

138
00:10:00,593 --> 00:10:01,184
<i>Naruto...!</i>

139
00:10:01,728 --> 00:10:03,195
Go, Naruto!

140
00:10:03,896 --> 00:10:05,796
What are you talking about,
bleeding like that?

141
00:10:06,265 --> 00:10:08,028
Your tough talk has gone too far!

142
00:10:09,035 --> 00:10:13,131
I didn't use my power fully...
to observe your strength first!

143
00:10:15,074 --> 00:10:18,635
You too, cut out the tough talk
and use the dog or whatever you want!

144
00:10:19,912 --> 00:10:21,470
You'll regret this...

145
00:10:22,749 --> 00:10:23,909
Let's go Akamaru!

146
00:10:30,056 --> 00:10:30,920
Smoke Ball?

147
00:10:31,290 --> 00:10:32,018
Take this!

148
00:10:53,846 --> 00:10:54,744
<i>I can't see!</i>

149
00:10:55,014 --> 00:10:55,844
<i>This is bad!</i>

150
00:10:56,349 --> 00:10:59,079
<i>I have to get out of the smoke...</i>
<i>or I'll be done for.</i>

151
00:11:02,822 --> 00:11:03,516
It worked!

152
00:11:07,326 --> 00:11:08,190
What is it...?

153
00:11:08,428 --> 00:11:10,896
Shoot... I can't see anything.

154
00:11:26,946 --> 00:11:28,846
Yeah! We did it!

155
00:11:30,650 --> 00:11:32,379
Yay! Good job, Akama!

156
00:11:44,363 --> 00:11:45,694
A-Akamaru...

157
00:11:46,299 --> 00:11:46,993
Why?

158
00:11:58,981 --> 00:11:59,879
Why?

159
00:12:01,316 --> 00:12:03,750
You took the bait!

160
00:12:06,989 --> 00:12:08,047
Y-You!

161
00:12:08,123 --> 00:12:08,987
Transform Jutsu?!

162
00:12:09,391 --> 00:12:10,915
Ouch! Shoot!

163
00:12:11,460 --> 00:12:12,085
Let go!

164
00:12:14,563 --> 00:12:16,224
You smell like a dog!

165
00:12:16,665 --> 00:12:18,860
W-Where's Akamaru?!

166
00:12:19,234 --> 00:12:20,201
Over here!

167
00:12:21,503 --> 00:12:23,937
Akamaru! Damn!

168
00:12:25,073 --> 00:12:25,732
No way!

169
00:12:26,108 --> 00:12:27,097
That's Naruto?!

170
00:12:27,876 --> 00:12:29,434
An equal match with Kiba...

171
00:12:29,678 --> 00:12:31,407
No, it may be more than equal!

172
00:12:31,747 --> 00:12:35,513
Applying Shadow Clone Jutsu
to Transform Jutsu, that's a clever trick.

173
00:12:35,918 --> 00:12:37,943
Naruto shouldn't be able to do that...

174
00:12:39,021 --> 00:12:41,546
His timing at using Jutsu's is very good.

175
00:12:41,757 --> 00:12:44,419
What? He's better than I thought.

176
00:12:46,628 --> 00:12:50,257
<i>But, to get mad like that after</i>
<i>biting the opponent himself...</i>

177
00:12:50,465 --> 00:12:51,693
<i>What a funny guy.</i>

178
00:12:53,302 --> 00:12:54,963
N-Naruto... amazing

179
00:12:55,037 --> 00:12:56,868
That's amazing, Naruto!

180
00:13:01,677 --> 00:13:04,976
You got a little bit stronger.

181
00:13:05,914 --> 00:13:07,211
But it's over.

182
00:13:07,950 --> 00:13:09,281
Next, I'll attack you seriously.

183
00:13:09,418 --> 00:13:11,079
Oh really?!

184
00:13:11,353 --> 00:13:14,914
But you will absolutely not beat me!

185
00:13:15,657 --> 00:13:18,182
<i>During this exam,</i>
<i>he's matured again.</i>

186
00:13:20,796 --> 00:13:22,559
This is a surprise...

187
00:13:24,533 --> 00:13:26,660
<i>That's Naruto, the perpetual goof...?</i>

188
00:13:27,235 --> 00:13:30,796
Evidently it's no longer "that" Naruto.

189
00:13:31,206 --> 00:13:31,695
Yeah.

190
00:13:33,041 --> 00:13:36,238
<i>I wonder, what kind</i>
<i>of trick Kakashi used...?</i>

191
00:13:37,980 --> 00:13:38,674
<i>Still...</i>

192
00:13:47,456 --> 00:13:47,979
Huh?

193
00:13:56,865 --> 00:13:58,924
<i>As for the development of</i>
<i>my Kiba and Akamaru,</i>

194
00:13:59,001 --> 00:14:00,229
<i>it's probably more than Naruto.</i>

195
00:14:02,771 --> 00:14:07,606
Naruto... I'll take Akamaru... back!

196
00:14:25,127 --> 00:14:26,287
W-What's this?!

197
00:14:26,495 --> 00:14:30,124
What did you feed him?
His fur turned red!

198
00:14:30,365 --> 00:14:33,027
That's why he's called "Akamaru", red boy.

199
00:14:34,770 --> 00:14:35,862
<i>Food Pills huh...?</i>

200
00:14:37,005 --> 00:14:37,994
<i>That Kiba...</i>

201
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,432
<i>He intends to end it with this.</i>

202
00:14:40,942 --> 00:14:42,102
Here we go, Akamaru!

203
00:14:44,579 --> 00:14:45,807
Ninja Art of Beast Mimicry!

204
00:14:57,059 --> 00:14:58,390
Man Beast Clones!

205
00:15:02,497 --> 00:15:04,761
T-There's something wrong
with their eyes!

206
00:15:04,966 --> 00:15:06,695
He's using some weird drug

207
00:15:07,169 --> 00:15:08,659
Isn't this doping?

208
00:15:08,737 --> 00:15:09,567
Is this okay?!

209
00:15:10,005 --> 00:15:13,304
Yes. Food Pills are one of Ninja Tools.

210
00:15:14,843 --> 00:15:16,470
You, that's all you say!

211
00:15:17,145 --> 00:15:18,112
What?!

212
00:15:18,447 --> 00:15:20,210
What did that guy eat?

213
00:15:20,682 --> 00:15:21,808
It's Food Pills.

214
00:15:22,350 --> 00:15:23,840
F-Food Pills?

215
00:15:24,753 --> 00:15:27,278
Food Pills are a secret medicine
that people in the military take

216
00:15:27,355 --> 00:15:31,314
and fight for three days and
three nights without a break...

217
00:15:31,993 --> 00:15:33,858
They're high in protein,
easily absorbed and

218
00:15:33,929 --> 00:15:38,764
have some types of component
that influence agitation or sedation...

219
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:46,273
Kiba and Akamaru's Chakra must
be doubled right now...

220
00:15:46,775 --> 00:15:48,072
It's over with this...

221
00:15:48,543 --> 00:15:49,271
Let's go!

222
00:15:49,811 --> 00:15:50,903
All Four...

223
00:15:51,513 --> 00:15:53,071
Jutsu!

224
00:16:14,903 --> 00:16:15,995
N-Naruto!

225
00:16:17,539 --> 00:16:20,030
That Naruto is in danger!

226
00:16:21,810 --> 00:16:24,210
Kiba's the gung ho fighter type
who will attack

227
00:16:24,279 --> 00:16:27,248
like a beast with Chakra wired
throughout his body.

228
00:16:28,517 --> 00:16:31,213
And the Food Pills that double one's
Chakra are quite simply...

229
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:34,018
the perfect pill for Kiba.

230
00:16:35,924 --> 00:16:36,913
<i>Naruto...</i>

231
00:16:39,995 --> 00:16:40,689
<i>This isn't good...</i>

232
00:16:41,163 --> 00:16:42,391
<i>There's no way to counterattack...</i>

233
00:16:42,797 --> 00:16:45,129
<i>All I can do is gather all</i>
<i>the Chakra in my legs</i>

234
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,792
<i>and do my best to escape...!</i>

235
00:16:47,135 --> 00:16:47,931
<i>At this rate...</i>

236
00:16:53,575 --> 00:16:54,337
Here's my chance!

237
00:16:55,610 --> 00:16:56,304
Take this!

238
00:16:56,378 --> 00:16:58,141
Man Beast Taijutsu Ultimate Technique!

239
00:17:02,317 --> 00:17:04,080
Fang Over Fang

240
00:17:19,467 --> 00:17:22,095
This is the difference in
our true powers.

241
00:17:30,912 --> 00:17:32,004
I'm going...

242
00:17:33,582 --> 00:17:34,708
to become the Hokage!

243
00:17:36,184 --> 00:17:38,175
I can't lose here...!

244
00:17:39,387 --> 00:17:40,945
You? Hokage?!

245
00:17:41,156 --> 00:17:42,987
When you're weaker than me?

246
00:17:44,893 --> 00:17:48,522
I'll become Hokage for you!

247
00:18:01,343 --> 00:18:05,404
You know deep down inside
that you can't become the Hokage.

248
00:18:06,114 --> 00:18:07,479
So quit acting tough!

249
00:18:12,721 --> 00:18:13,847
You're wrong, Kiba...

250
00:18:16,291 --> 00:18:17,223
<i>Naruto...</i>

251
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:19,852
<i>He's not that weak...</i>

252
00:18:21,763 --> 00:18:26,860
I'll receive the name...
of Lord Hokage!

253
00:18:29,738 --> 00:18:32,536
All of you, just watch!

254
00:18:33,475 --> 00:18:36,035
<i>Naruto, unlike me...</i>

255
00:18:36,878 --> 00:18:38,812
<i>he has always believed in his own worth.</i>

256
00:18:50,992 --> 00:18:53,324
<i>I thought it was really amazing...</i>

257
00:18:54,362 --> 00:18:56,853
<i>It must have been really hard...</i>

258
00:19:04,439 --> 00:19:06,600
<i>I understand that.</i>

259
00:19:08,143 --> 00:19:10,941
<i>And yet before not even one person...</i>

260
00:19:15,417 --> 00:19:17,510
<i>tried to see Naruto.</i>

261
00:19:23,558 --> 00:19:25,048
Hey, that's the kid...

262
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:29,521
I heard he's the only one...
who failed.

263
00:19:30,098 --> 00:19:31,827
Humph! Serves him right!

264
00:19:32,334 --> 00:19:34,859
It's trouble if a kid like that
becomes a Ninja.

265
00:19:35,303 --> 00:19:36,565
After all, that kid is really...

266
00:19:36,638 --> 00:19:39,004
Stop! Anything further is taboo.

267
00:19:41,976 --> 00:19:44,740
<i>Nobody tried to acknowledge</i>
<i>real Naruto.</i>

268
00:19:53,154 --> 00:19:54,519
Clone Jutsu!

269
00:20:07,936 --> 00:20:08,903
<i>But now...</i>

270
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:13,629
<i>Everyone's watching...</i>

271
00:20:22,117 --> 00:20:23,311
Stand up! Naruto!

272
00:20:30,024 --> 00:20:31,423
<i>Everyone is acknowledging him!</i>

273
00:20:46,241 --> 00:20:49,642
If you compete with me for
the name of Hokage...

274
00:20:51,746 --> 00:20:55,113
You... will be the loser!

275
00:21:06,733 --> 00:21:11,193
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

276
00:21:11,338 --> 00:21:19,677
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

277
00:21:20,681 --> 00:21:29,350
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

278
00:21:29,756 --> 00:21:37,595
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

279
00:21:38,865 --> 00:21:44,269
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

280
00:21:44,338 --> 00:21:48,365
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

281
00:21:48,442 --> 00:21:52,003
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

282
00:21:52,346 --> 00:22:00,879
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

283
00:22:01,154 --> 00:22:06,353
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

284
00:22:06,426 --> 00:22:10,829
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

285
00:22:10,897 --> 00:22:14,663
<i>Just sing.</i>

286
00:22:14,901 --> 00:22:20,066
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

287
00:22:20,140 --> 00:22:22,335
<i>The two are one</i>

288
00:22:22,442 --> 00:22:28,711
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

289
00:22:29,216 --> 00:22:34,313
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

290
00:22:38,669 --> 00:22:41,001
That Kiba, he sure is stupid.

291
00:22:41,072 --> 00:22:43,370
Think hard about your Jutsu
when you use them.

292
00:22:43,508 --> 00:22:46,443
Otherwise, your opponents
will take advantage of the Jutsu.

293
00:22:46,544 --> 00:22:50,207
Well, the outcome of you and me
could be seen from the beginning.

294
00:22:50,381 --> 00:22:52,679
The way you've torn me apart
up until now,

295
00:22:52,784 --> 00:22:55,218
I'll give it back all at once!

296
00:22:55,920 --> 00:23:00,050
Next episode: "Surprise Attack!
Naruto's Secret Weapon!"

297
00:23:00,291 --> 00:23:02,725
This is the trick I've been saving up!
